@@TJvParaAttributesRec
<TITLE TJvParaAttributesRec type>
Summary
  Stores paragraph attributes.
Description
  TJvParaAttributesRec is a record type used to store paragraph attributes for RTF-encoded values in
  a rich edit control.
  
  Use the Alignment and Numbering members to access or update the text alignment and numbering styles
  for content occurring in the paragraph.
  
  TJvParaAttributesRec is similar to TJvRichEditParaAttributesRec which implements additional
  paragraph alignment and numbering styles.
  
  TJvParaAttributesRec and TJvRichEditParaAttributesRec are used in methods in the TJvRichEditToHtml
  component when converting RTF content to HTML.
See Also
  TJvRichEditParaAttributesRec, TJvRichEditToHtml.ConvertToHtmlStrings

